des: "It smells good when it's cooked. Cut in wedges, and serve with jasmine rice. You can have it anytime! If you like spicy, put in some chile sauce."
ins: Heat oil in a wok or skillet over medium heat. In a medium bowl, whisk together eggs, fish sauce, pepper and ground pork. When oil is hot, pour in egg mixture. Fry until fully cooked, and golden on both sides.
